        {
            "title": "20個指標屋苑一年轉手率介乎2.2%至4.8%｜嘉亨灣4.8%居首｜康怡花園、寶翠園並列第二",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">28Hse最新追蹤的20個指標屋苑*成交記錄冊顯示，截至4月，屋苑一年的二手轉手率**介乎2.2%至4.8%。當中，<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"西灣河嘉亨灣\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:西灣河嘉亨灣;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4aWWQXk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">西灣河嘉亨灣</a>的轉手率最高，達4.8%；<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"鰂魚涌康怡花園\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:鰂魚涌康怡花園;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/3McZEHA\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">鰂魚涌康怡花園</a>及<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"堅尼地城寶翠園\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:堅尼地城寶翠園;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4p1cXIc\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">堅尼地城寶翠園</a>同為3.9%，並列第二。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析指，轉手率較高的三個屋苑同樣位於港島，交通及景觀條件較佳，一向具市場吸引力，買家以中產家庭及換樓客為主。隨着樓市氣氛向好，資金傾向流向傳統港島地段，帶動區內交投上升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">閱讀更多：</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"西灣河嘉亨灣3房以月租$2.8萬 實用呎租$56.4 (另有本日最新成交)\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:西灣河嘉亨灣3房以月租$2.8萬 實用呎租$56.4 (另有本日最新成交);elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4tIF4Pi\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">西灣河嘉亨灣3房以月租$2.8萬 實用呎租$56.4 (另有本日最新成交)</a></p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-880befae-52e7-3467-9723-55d2ee2b7009-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"西灣河嘉亨灣一日內連沽5伙 兩伙3房套分別大賺7球！\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:西灣河嘉亨灣一日內連沽5伙 兩伙3房套分別大賺7球！;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4sApi8e\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">西灣河嘉亨灣一日內連沽5伙 兩伙3房套分別大賺7球！</a></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/11TyaaDjRfmjxX1gzjCPKQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/dc3b422c661914054c321c1f9e63d040\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>嘉亨灣過去一年轉手率居首 二手交投錄96宗</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"28Hse數據\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:28Hse數據;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4aWWQXk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">28Hse數據</a>顯示，西灣河嘉亨灣為一年二手轉手率最高的屋苑，轉手率達4.8%，期內錄得96宗二手成交。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">至於近90日表現，屋苑錄得30宗二手成交，其平均成交呎價為20,717元，按期升5.83%，獲利成交比例約76%。現時屋苑約有32個放盤，叫價介乎700萬至3,380萬元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">租務方面，嘉亨灣近90日錄得72宗租賃成交，平均租金回報率約3%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"【即睇嘉亨灣放盤】\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:【即睇嘉亨灣放盤】;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4aWWQXk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【即睇嘉亨灣放盤】</a></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/UFjV5_7Yx6ybqcZZTlsFDw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/23c6dc1cd5876d705ae8155f16596c6f\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>嘉亨灣</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>康怡花園及寶翠園轉手率同錄3.9% 並列第二</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"鰂魚涌康怡花園\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:鰂魚涌康怡花園;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/3McZEHA\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">鰂魚涌康怡花園</a>及<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"堅尼地城寶翠園\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:堅尼地城寶翠園;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4p1cXIc\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">堅尼地城寶翠園</a>，為過去一年二手轉手率第二高的屋苑，轉手率同錄3.9%，期內分別錄得207宗及82宗二手成交。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>➢ 康怡花園近90日錄69宗成交</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"鰂魚涌康怡花園\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:鰂魚涌康怡花園;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/3McZEHA\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">鰂魚涌康怡花園</a>近90日錄得69宗二手成交，獲利成交比例約78%。目前屋苑約有118個放盤，叫價介乎550萬至1,800萬元。租務方面，屋苑同期錄得43宗租賃成交，平均租金回報率約3.6%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"【即睇康怡花園放盤】\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:【即睇康怡花園放盤】;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/3McZEHA\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【即睇康怡花園放盤】</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>➢ 寶翠園近90日錄18宗成交</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"堅尼地城寶翠園\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:堅尼地城寶翠園;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4p1cXIc\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">堅尼地城寶翠園</a>近90日錄得18宗二手成交，獲利成交比例約89%。目前屋苑約有46個放盤，叫價介乎1,400萬至4,400萬元。租務方面，屋苑同期錄得35宗租賃成交，平均租金回報率約2.7%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"【即睇寶翠園放盤】\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:【即睇寶翠園放盤】;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4p1cXIc\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【即睇寶翠園放盤】</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>黃埔花園一年轉手率錄3.8% 位列其後</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">至於其餘藍籌屋苑，<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"紅磡黃埔花園\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:紅磡黃埔花園;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/3Yy1Sng\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">紅磡黃埔花園</a>一年二手轉手率為3.8%，排行第四。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"【即睇黃埔花園放盤】\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:【即睇黃埔花園放盤】;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/3Yy1Sng\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【即睇黃埔花園放盤】</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>購買力回流港島 換樓客加快入市</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">今年樓價穩步上升，帶動整體市場氣氛，部分資金流向港島傳統屋苑。嘉亨灣、康怡花園及寶翠園屬區內指標物業，具備海景或鄰近港鐵站等地理條件，社區配套發展成熟。這類物業的客源以中產家庭為主，數據反映，不少換樓客因應市況向好而加快入市步伐，帶動上述港島屋苑的交投上升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>租務交投活躍 回報率具防守力</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">除自住需求外，穩定的租務市場亦是帶動轉手率的因素之一。港島區屋苑租客多為專業人士及外籍人士，租務需求相對平穩。上述三個屋苑近期租務交投保持活躍，平均租金回報率介乎2.7%至3.6%。在現時市況下，相關回報率對部分長線投資者具吸引力，帶動收租投資需求。在自住及投資客源帶動下，整體二手轉手率有所提升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">*20個指標屋苑包括：太古城、康怡花園、海怡半島、嘉亨灣、藍灣半島、寶翠園、南豐新邨、映灣園、嘉湖山莊、沙田第一城、新都城、新港城、珀麗灣、盈翠半島、荃威花園、美孚新邨、麗港城、德福花園、碧海藍天及黃埔花園</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">** 一年轉手率 = 屋苑過去一年二手成交總宗數 ÷ 屋苑單位總數</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀: <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"沙田第一城\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:沙田第一城;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/沙田第一城-4080\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">沙田第一城</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"德福花園\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:德福花園;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/德福花園-2080\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">德福花園</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"嘉湖山莊\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:嘉湖山莊;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/嘉湖山莊-4390\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">嘉湖山莊</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"盈翠半島\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:盈翠半島;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/盈翠半島-4650\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">盈翠半島</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkTe